<div class="container-fluid">

<% if session[:user_id] && @pitch.job_id.nil? %>
  <b> Share this Pitch: </b> <br>
  <%= @pitch.url_string %>
<%end%>

<p class="lead">Copy this Pitch link: <%=link_to "Link for employer",  @pitch.url_string %></p>

<% if session[:employer_id]%>
    <b>Like what you see? </b>
    <br> Email this candidate: <%= link_to @pitch.user.email, email_url(@pitch.id)%>
<%end%>

<% @video_link1 = "http://www.youtube.com/embed/YpugK0RpEaU" %>
<% @video_link2 = "http://www.youtube.com/embed/QjlFqgRbICY" %>

<div class="jumbotron">
        <h4><%=@pitch.user.first_name.capitalize %>'personal pitch</h4>
        <% if session[:user_id] && @pitch.job_id.nil? %>
        
        <h1 class="row-fluid span4"><%= @pitch.headline%></h1>

        <div class="row-fluid span12">
          <%= image_tag @pitch.avatar_url(:thumb).to_s, :size=>'100x100', :class => "row-fluid span2"%>
          <p class="row-fluid span8"><b><%= @pitch.user.first_name.capitalize%>'s Story:</b> In a previous life I was a cancer researcher. My life was dedicated to improve the lives of our patients.  After 7 years, I discovered a love for programming.  I started graviatingn more and more with the progammers.  My sister introduced me to Codecademy's online learning system.  I was hooked.  I finally reached a point where I was tired of playing in sandboxes and wanted to actually create.  That's why I applied to The Starter League in Chicago.  Upon my acceptance, I resigned from my job, sold my house, packed my bags and flew to Chicago.   </p>
        </div>
          
        <%end%>
      

      <hr>
  
      <div class="row-fluid span12">
        <div class="row-fluid span4 flex-video widescreen"><iframe width="100%" src= "<%=@video_link2%>" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>
      
      
    

        <div class="row-fluid span8 marketing">
          <div class="span6">

            <% @even_index_prompts.each do |prompt_object| %>

            <h4><%= prompt_object.custom_question %></h4>
            <p><%= prompt_object.custom_answer %></p>

            <%end%>

          </div>

          <div class="span6">
            <% @odd_index_prompts.each do |prompt_object| %>

            <h4><%= prompt_object.custom_question %></h4>
            <p><%= prompt_object.custom_answer %></p>

            <%end%>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row-fluid span12">

        <div class="row-fluid span4">
          <%= link_to image_tag("doc_icon.png"), '#'%>
        </div>
        <div class="row-fluid span4">
          <%= link_to image_tag("folder_icon.png"), '#'%>
        </div>
        <div class="row-fluid span4">
          
        </div>

      </div>
</div>
